<subSubSection id="1C9165094144FFCAFF03B27487ECF85B" lastPageId="1" lastPageNumber="63" pageId="0" pageNumber="62" type="description">
<paragraph id="543436824144FFCBFF03B27484A1F940" blockId="0.[136,1452,1568,2026]" pageId="0" pageNumber="62">
This is a new record for 
<collectingCountry id="2C9C76124144FFCBFE2AB2748718F9F8" box="[417,512,1568,1594]" name="Ethiopia" pageId="0" pageNumber="62">Ethiopia</collectingCountry>
(
<figureCitation id="CCB02A074144FFCBFD9BB274874AF9F8" box="[528,594,1568,1594]" captionStart="FIGURE 1" captionStartId="1.[136,229,960,982]" captionTargetBox="[354,1230,200,919]" captionTargetId="figure-20@1.[340,1247,187,933]" captionTargetPageId="1" captionText="FIGURE 1. Map of the Horn of Africa region, showing the distribution of Cystostemon heliocharis." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5308329" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5308329/files/figure.png" pageId="0" pageNumber="62">Fig. 1</figureCitation>
). The previously unidentified material was included among specimens sent from the South East Rangelands project in 
<collectingCountry id="2C9C76124144FFCBFDFAB21087C8F99C" box="[625,720,1604,1630]" name="Ethiopia" pageId="0" pageNumber="62">Ethiopia</collectingCountry>
to UPS. The collection was made in open shrubland on a northfacing slope of a stony hill.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="543436824144FFCBFF36B2D881E4F92D" blockId="0.[136,1452,1568,2026]" pageId="0" pageNumber="62">
The genus 
<taxonomicName id="938B4D014144FFCBFEB7B2D887B1F964" authority="Balfour (1884: 82)" authorityName="Balfour" authorityPageNumber="82" authorityYear="1884" box="[316,681,1676,1702]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Boraginaceae" genus="Cystostemon" kingdom="Plantae" order="Boraginales" pageId="0" pageNumber="62" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="66FFEA904144FFCBFEB7B2D884D3F964" box="[316,459,1676,1702]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="62">Cystostemon</emphasis>
Balfour (1884: 82)
</taxonomicName>
was revised by 
<bibRefCitation id="301A4B734144FFCBFCEEB2D8817CF964" author="Miller, A. G. &amp; Riedl, H." box="[869,1124,1676,1702]" pageId="0" pageNumber="62" pagination="1 - 21" refId="ref2845" refString="Miller, A. G. &amp; Riedl, H. (1982) A revision of Cystostemon Balf. f. (Boraginaceae). Notes from the Royal Botanic Garden Edinburgh 40: 1 - 21." type="journal article" year="1982">Miller &amp; Riedl (1982)</bibRefCitation>
, who recognized 13 species, distributed from the southwestern Arabian Peninsula and 
<collectingCountry id="2C9C76124144FFCBFC96B2E4866BF908" box="[797,883,1712,1738]" name="Yemen" pageId="0" pageNumber="62">Socotra</collectingCountry>
in the north, to 
<collectingCountry id="2C9C76124144FFCBFBBAB2E4819FF908" box="[1073,1159,1712,1738]" name="Zambia" pageId="0" pageNumber="62">Zambia</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry id="2C9C76124144FFCBFB4AB2E4800BF908" box="[1217,1299,1712,1738]" name="Angola" pageId="0" pageNumber="62">Angola</collectingCountry>
in the south. Since then, three further species have been described from 
<collectingCountry id="2C9C76124144FFCBFC90B2808675F92C" box="[795,877,1748,1774]" name="Angola" pageId="0" pageNumber="62">Angola</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry id="2C9C76124144FFCBFC2FB28086E2F92C" box="[932,1018,1748,1774]" name="Zambia" pageId="0" pageNumber="62">Zambia</collectingCountry>
by 
<bibRefCitation id="301A4B734144FFCBFBAFB28081CAF92C" author="Martins, E. S." box="[1060,1234,1748,1774]" pageId="0" pageNumber="62" pagination="1 - 2" refId="ref2768" refString="Martins, E. S. (1988 a) Cystostemon loveridgei E. S. Martins and C. mwinilungensis E. S. Martins. Garcia de Orta, Serie de Botanica 9 (1 - 2): 75." type="journal article" year="1988">Martins (1988a</bibRefCitation>
, b).
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="543436824144FFCBFF36B2AC84A2F828" blockId="0.[136,1452,1568,2026]" pageId="0" pageNumber="62">
<bibRefCitation id="301A4B734144FFCBFF36B2AC84AAF8D0" author="Miller, A. G. &amp; Riedl, H." box="[189,434,1784,1810]" pageId="0" pageNumber="62" pagination="1 - 21" refId="ref2845" refString="Miller, A. G. &amp; Riedl, H. (1982) A revision of Cystostemon Balf. f. (Boraginaceae). Notes from the Royal Botanic Garden Edinburgh 40: 1 - 21." type="journal article" year="1982">Miller &amp; Riedl (1982)</bibRefCitation>
cited material of 
<taxonomicName id="938B4D014144FFCBFDFFB2AC869FF8D0" authorityName="A. G. Mill. &amp; Riedl" authorityYear="1982" baseAuthorityName="S. Moore" box="[628,903,1784,1810]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Boraginaceae" genus="Cystostemon" kingdom="Plantae" order="Boraginales" pageId="0" pageNumber="62" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="heliocharis">
<emphasis id="66FFEA904144FFCBFDFFB2AC869FF8D0" box="[628,903,1784,1810]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="62">Cystostemon heliocharis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
from 
<collectingCountry id="2C9C76124144FFCBFC43B2AD810EF8D1" box="[968,1046,1785,1811]" name="Yemen" pageId="0" pageNumber="62">Yemen</collectingCountry>
and 
<collectingCountry id="2C9C76124144FFCBFBC0B2AC81B2F8D0" box="[1099,1194,1784,1810]" name="Somalia" pageId="0" pageNumber="62">Somalia</collectingCountry>
, and provided a map of the distribution of the species. 
<bibRefCitation id="301A4B734144FFCBFE54B3488790F8F5" author="Thulin, M." box="[479,648,1820,1847]" pageId="0" pageNumber="62" pagination="53 - 54" refId="ref3401" refString="Thulin, M. (2006 a) Cystostemon. In: Thulin, M. (Ed.) Flora of Somalia, vol. 3. Royal Botanic Gardens, Kew, pp. 53 - 54." type="book chapter" year="2006">Thulin (2006a)</bibRefCitation>
treated four species, 
<emphasis id="66FFEA904144FFCBFCFDB3488103F8F4" box="[886,1051,1820,1846]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="62">
<taxonomicName id="938B4D014144FFCBFCFDB348810FF8F4" authorityName="A. G. Mill. &amp; Riedl" authorityYear="1982" baseAuthorityName="S. Moore" box="[886,1047,1820,1846]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Boraginaceae" genus="Cystostemon" kingdom="Plantae" order="Boraginales" pageId="0" pageNumber="62" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="heliocharis">C. heliocharis</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
<taxonomicName id="938B4D014144FFCBFBA9B34885B6F898" authority="Miller &amp; Riedl (1982: 11)" authorityName="Miller &amp; Riedl" authorityPageNumber="11" authorityYear="1982" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Boraginaceae" genus="Cystostemon" kingdom="Plantae" order="Boraginales" pageId="0" pageNumber="62" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="intricatus">
<emphasis id="66FFEA904144FFCBFBA9B34881B6F8F4" box="[1058,1198,1820,1846]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="62">C. intricatus</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="301A4B734144FFCBFB3EB34885B6F898" author="Miller, A. G. &amp; Riedl, H." pageId="0" pageNumber="62" pagination="1 - 21" refId="ref2845" refString="Miller, A. G. &amp; Riedl, H. (1982) A revision of Cystostemon Balf. f. (Boraginaceae). Notes from the Royal Botanic Garden Edinburgh 40: 1 - 21." type="journal article" year="1982">Miller &amp; Riedl (1982: 11)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="938B4D014144FFCBFF31B3148761F898" authority="Miller &amp; Riedl (1982: 8)" authorityName="Miller &amp; Riedl" authorityPageNumber="8" authorityYear="1982" box="[186,633,1856,1882]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Boraginaceae" genus="Cystostemon" kingdom="Plantae" order="Boraginales" pageId="0" pageNumber="62" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="somaliensis">
<emphasis id="66FFEA904144FFCBFF31B3148445F898" box="[186,349,1856,1882]" italics="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="62">C. somaliensis</emphasis>
<bibRefCitation id="301A4B734144FFCBFEEFB3148761F898" author="Miller, A. G. &amp; Riedl, H." box="[356,633,1856,1882]" pageId="0" pageNumber="62" pagination="1 - 21" refId="ref2845" refString="Miller, A. G. &amp; Riedl, H. (1982) A revision of Cystostemon Balf. f. (Boraginaceae). Notes from the Royal Botanic Garden Edinburgh 40: 1 - 21." type="journal article" year="1982">Miller &amp; Riedl (1982: 8)</bibRefCitation>
</taxonomicName>
, and 
<taxonomicName id="938B4D014144FFCBFD3FB314817CF899" authority="Miller &amp; Riedl (1982: 15)" authorityName="Miller &amp; Riedl" authorityPageNumber="15" authorityYear="1982" box="[692,1124,1856,1883]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Boraginaceae" genus="Cystostemon" kingdom="Plantae" order="Boraginales" pageId="0" pageNumber="62" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="virescens">
