(Somaliland). A photograph of a plant from a locality in northwestern 
<collectingCountry id="2C9C76124144FFCBFF03B38485FCF828" box="[136,228,2000,2026]" name="Somalia" pageId="0" pageNumber="62">Somalia</collectingCountry>
